metadata.name: Canigro
metadata.description:
CANIGRO 

A classic space and time bender. You go in and never know where or when you will come out. Bored of routine? This is the one for you.

Although each dark hole has a different character, all tend to hypnotize and stun you, drag you into themselves, unpromising predictability. 

Just stare at the loop forever or enter the void at your own will. 

2160 X 2160px
.mp4

Audio and video loops seamlessly if played in repeat.






UNBUILd is a collaborative group of award winning artists, architects and sound designers. 

The audiovisual artworks involve various techniques such as hand illustrations, 3D arts, animations and photography combined with musical sounds uniquely designed and generated by analog synths, stringed instruments and effects.
